q3.value:
This systematic review is in accordance to the PRISMA statement. The “PICOs” for this systematic review is defined as:
Population: specimens with any geometry comprising Y-TZP framework;
Intervention: veneering technique based on Cad-on or overpressing procedures;
Comparison: manual layering veneering method;
Outcomes: Shear, microtensile and retentive bond strengths;
Study design: in vitro studies.

